WO 2004/010957, published February 5, 2004

, and 

WO2006/034488, published September 9, 2005

 (each of which patent applications is herein incorporated by reference in its entirety). Prior to conjugation, the antibodies were partially reduced with TCEP using standard methods in accordance with the methodology described in 

